room_title: Escape room "Wanted Dead or Alive" by Axxiom Escape Rooms in Newark
room_address: 280 E Main Street Unit 132, Newark, DE 19711
room_description: A fierce wind blows across the plains ad carries whispers throughout Tombstone, the town of lawlessness.  A frontier town crippled with fear by outlaws... yet one sheriff is determined to restore order. With your help, we can bring the outlaws to justice and end their reign of terror. Four outlaws... one hiding place.  Step back in time into the old west and bring your cowboy boots. It's a new day and there's a new sheriff in town.
